cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL

This paper deals with regularization techniques for deep neural networks in the context of image recognition tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also proposes a novel method for regularization, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CL (Computation and Language) depending on the specific focus of the method.
